    "style": "light",
    "content": "具体的アクション4つ",
    "html": "<style>@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;700;900&display=swap');*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a2e2e}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:20px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);border-radius:20px;padding:4px 16px;font-size:15px;color:#0d6e6e}.logo{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d6e6e}.main{padding:10px 60px;height:560px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}.section-label{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;letter-spacing:4px;margin-bottom:16px}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:24px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;margin-bottom:18px}.list-num{min-width:44px;height:44px;background:#14b8a6;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#fff}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.5;padding-top:6px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 40px;font-size:14px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">SLIDE 05</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><span class=\"section-label\">結 ── 臨床での実践</span><h2>明日からできる4つのアクション</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><p class=\"list-text\">LibreView / Dexcom ClarityのAGPレポートを日常的に活用する</p></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><p class=\"list-text\">処方選択時に臨床データ（BMI, HbA1c, eGFR, CV risk）を構造化記録</p></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><p class=\"list-text\">患者向けAIアプリの基本知識を持ち「治療判断には使わない」と説明</p></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">4</span><p class=\"list-text\">AIは支援ツール -- 最終判断は目の前の患者を診ている医師が行う</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
